>2018</date></imprint><biblScope unit="pp">116</biblScope></monogr></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb10815">Bahr, Hermann</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">[Wien]</placeName><date when="1896-02-05" n="01">5. 2. [1896]</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">[Wien]</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10815">Bahr, Hermann</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1895-10-12_01">Bahr an Schnitzler, [12. 10. 1895]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1896-02-07_01">Schnitzler an Bahr, 7. 2. 1896</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
